1402:An individual member must:
1404:- Avail, directly or indirectly, services offered by SFPCL during membership.
1405:- Supply primary produce for a continuous period of four financial years as on the last date of previous financial year to SFPCL, subsidiaries, step-down subsidiaries or through a Producer Institution member that supplies to these entities.
